{
  "stem": "25651.11",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The stories were all the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you sort of got bored with it all, because it's-- it's all the same.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- the fact that it varies a little bit here and there is of no consequence, because it's all the same.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's all-- it's all this grinding death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this man is quite mad, because he's-- he's talking about losing his family all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, he's not reconciled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we're walking into his [INAUDIBLE] atelier-- into the-- his atelier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he had a whole barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was all sunny, you know, in the summer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Beautiful for painting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they chat about art, which I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't know all these things about Bach, or Mozart, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They could have talked about China for all I-- for all I knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I was a lad of 14 who hadn't been to school for four years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mengele says to this officer Schwartzenberg, he says, tell you what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since you're going to the front, I'll get this painter to paint him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He points at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he gives the command to the painter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, you're gonna make a portrait of him and we're going to send it to Berlin to the apartment of Obersturmbannfuhrer Von Schwartzenberg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A present.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the significant thing was that Schwartzenberg had been with us some 10 days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In that time, he organized for me to grow my hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mengele tried to impress him about his civilization, and his sort of interesting art, and this music.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were talking about the orchestra at the gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this painter, you know, he's established a painter to paint pictures, because we don't kill artists.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
